{
  "stem": "5654.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And two days later, we were sitting in the dining room in the home.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And this couple came in with the police, and so on, and speaking to Mr.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Dybnis, our director.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We want to see a gentleman by the name of Leon.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was over there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They pointed that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Come over here.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they came in with a big cake, chocolate cake.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They gave me that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they said, we want to thank you very much for being honest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So you see, it paid dividends.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And, of course, they had started to invite me on Sundays.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They lived not far from the home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they said, please come-- come to eat at our place on Sunday.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And of course, I had to have the permission to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they gave me a pair of skis, which was very nice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And so, you know, of course, in the home, whenever we had something, we had to share with everybody.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because, you know, chocolates, we hadn't seen chocolate since before the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So it was really fantastic to have that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And because of that, the-- the the other-- what are called-- the population around, you know, being a small village, must have heard.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they became more and more friendly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So they give us things, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They send fruit and the things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You know, it was good.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we stayed till 1945.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And in 19--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, for two years.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was 19-- yeah, still the war finished.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Early-- and then the Swiss started to tell all the refugee, please get out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Go back to your country.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So with-- with Miriam and Henri Dybnis, we all closed the home, took a train to back to France.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
